.TH "nvme_init_get_log_changed_alloc_ns" 9 "nvme_init_get_log_changed_alloc_ns" "April 2026" "libnvme API manual" LINUX
.SH NAME
nvme_init_get_log_changed_alloc_ns \- Initialize passthru command for Changed Allocated Namespace List
.SH SYNOPSIS
.B "void" nvme_init_get_log_changed_alloc_ns
.BI "(struct libnvme_passthru_cmd *cmd "  ","
.BI "struct nvme_ns_list *log "  ","
.BI "__u32 len "  ");"
.SH ARGUMENTS
.IP "cmd" 12
Passthru command to use
.IP "log" 12
User address to store the log page
.IP "len" 12
The allocated length of the log page
.SH "DESCRIPTION"
Initializes the passthru command buffer for the Get Log command with
LID value NVME_LOG_LID_CHANGED_ALLOC_NS
